  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe \u0b90.\u0b93.\u0b9a\u0bbf - \u0b87\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Lanka IOC suspended fuel supply - this is the reason!",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Lanka IOC in the country Lanka IOC has stopped the supply of fuel to the filling stations. The company said.",
        "Lanka IOC We have decided to suspend the supply of fuel to the company's filling stations today (8) and tomorrow (9) due to security reasons.",
        "There will be continuous fuel supply to Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation and all industries.",
        "However, a spokesperson of the company added that fuel supply to the filling stations will resume from Monday."
      ],
